#   Enable "YouTube Data API v3" for the project, then create an API key.
#   Restrict it to "HTTP referrers" (your domain) and to the YouTube Data API.
#
# VITE_YT_CHANNEL_ID
#   The channel handle is @DrSyedAsifRazaZaidiOfficial.
#   To find the UCxxxxxx channel ID:
#     1. Go to https://www.youtube.com/@DrSyedAsifRazaZaidiOfficial
#     2. Right-click the page → View Page Source
#     3. Search (Ctrl+F) for "channelId" — copy the value starting with "UC"
#   OR visit https://www.youtube.com/@DrSyedAsifRazaZaidiOfficial/about
#     and look at the Share Channel link.
#
# If VITE_YT_API_KEY is left empty the site will automatically fall back to
# embedding the channel's public Uploads playlist (no API key needed).
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

